- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The robot is equipped with sensors and computing power to support researchers in many fields, including AI. 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science): There is no explicit mention of logic in the paper, but the robot's software is open-source and may involve logical reasoning. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper discusses the design and operation of a robotic system, which falls under the scope of this sub-category. 
- cs.MA (Multiagent Systems): The robot can potentially be used in multiagent systems research, such as in the context of RoboCup competitions.
